name: PromptBidder
description: Promptbidder is a advertisement service that connects businesses with people who are searching the problem they solve on ChatGPT and Perplexity. Co-Founders Rohan Arora and Venkat Krishnan got their startup back by Y Combinator in 2023, and more to add on to the funding list. With the product being released fully functional by Thursday July 10th we've seen a lot more interest from large clients.
